{
  "entries": [
    {
      "audio": "page1_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "むかしむかし、あるところに、",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Once upon a time, in a certain place,",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "とても貧しいおじいさんとおばあさんが住んでいました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "lived a very poor old man and old woman.",
      "prompt": "[calmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "二人はいつも仲が良く、助け合って暮らしていました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page1_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The two were always on good terms and lived helping each other.",
      "prompt": "[calmly, warmly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ある寒い冬の日、おじいさんは町へ行くことにしました。",
      "prompt": "[calmly, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "One cold winter day, the old man decided to go to town.",
      "prompt": "[calmly, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おばあさんは、おじいさんのために温かいおやつを作って持たせてあげました。",
      "prompt": "[warmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The old woman made warm snacks for the old man to take.",
      "prompt": "[warmly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "町に着いたおじいさんは、自分で作った竹細工を売ろうとしました。",
      "prompt": "[hopeful, slightly disappointed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "When the old man arrived in town, he tried to sell the bamboo crafts he made.",
      "prompt": "[hopeful, slightly disappointed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "でも、その日はとても寒くて、誰も買ってくれる人はいませんでした。",
      "prompt": "[sadly, disappointed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page2_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "But, it was very cold that day, and no one bought anything.",
      "prompt": "[sadly, disappointed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "がっかりしておじいさんが家に帰ろうとしたとき、",
      "prompt": "[sadly, disappointed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "As the disappointed old man was about to go home,",
      "prompt": "[sadly, disappointed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "お寺の前に、いくつかのお地蔵さまが立っているのが見えました。",
      "prompt": "[surprised, curious]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "he saw several Jizo statues standing in front of a temple.",
      "prompt": "[surprised, curious]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "お地蔵さまは、冷たい雪をかぶって、とても寒そうでした。",
      "prompt": "[sympathetically, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The Jizo statues were covered in cold snow and looked very cold.",
      "prompt": "[sympathetically, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「かわいそうだなぁ。お地蔵さまも、さぞかし寒いだろう。」",
      "prompt": "[sympathetically, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page3_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"How pitiful. The Jizo must be very cold.\"",
      "prompt": "[sympathetically, sadly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ふと、おじいさんの背中には、おばあさんが作ってくれた、あたたかい笠がいくつかありました。",
      "prompt": "[realization, hopeful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Suddenly, the old man remembered the warm hats his wife had made, which were on his back.",
      "prompt": "[realization, hopeful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「そうだ！この笠をお地蔵さまにかぶせてあげよう。」",
      "prompt": "[decided, excited]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"That's it! I'll put these hats on the Jizo statues.\"",
      "prompt": "[decided, excited]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんは、持っていた笠を一つずつ、お地蔵さまにかぶせてあげました。",
      "prompt": "[gently, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The old man put the hats one by one onto the Jizo statues.",
      "prompt": "[gently, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "ところが、笠が一つ足りなくなってしまいました。",
      "prompt": "[worried, concerned]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page4_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "However, they ran out of hats, with one Jizo left uncovered.",
      "prompt": "[worried, concerned]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「どうしよう。一つだけ笠がないのは、かわいそうだ。」",
      "prompt": "[worried, concerned]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"What should I do? It's pitiful for just one Jizo to be without a hat.\"",
      "prompt": "[worried, concerned]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんは、困ってしまいました。",
      "prompt": "[troubled, worried]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The old man was troubled.",
      "prompt": "[troubled, worried]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そこで、自分の持っていた手ぬぐいをほどいて、残ったお地蔵さまにかぶせてあげました。",
      "prompt": "[resourceful, kind]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "So, he unraveled his own towel and put it on the remaining Jizo.",
      "prompt": "[resourceful, kind]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そして、おじいさんは、お地蔵さまに「さむくないかい？あたらしい笠だよ」と話しかけながら、家路につきました。",
      "prompt": "[tenderly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page5_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Then, the old man headed home, talking to the Jizo, \"Aren't you cold? This is a new hat.\"",
      "prompt": "[tenderly, gently]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "家に帰ったおじいさんから話を聞いたおばあさんは、",
      "prompt": "[listening, understanding]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The old woman, after hearing the story from the old man who returned home,",
      "prompt": "[listening, understanding]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「まあ、なんて優しいおじいさん！お地蔵さまも喜んだだろうね」と、おじいさんの行動を喜びました。",
      "prompt": "[praising, happy]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Oh, what a kind old man! The Jizo must have been happy too,\" and rejoiced in the old man's actions.",
      "prompt": "[praising, happy]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "その夜、おじいさんとおばあさんが寝ていると、家の戸がトントンと鳴りました。",
      "prompt": "[peaceful, then startled]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "That night, as the old man and woman were sleeping, there was a knock, knock, knock on their door.",
      "prompt": "[peaceful, then startled]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「どなたでしょう？」",
      "prompt": "[curious, slightly fearful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page6_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Who could it be?\"",
      "prompt": "[curious, slightly fearful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんが戸を開けると、そこにはなんと、",
      "prompt": "[surprised, astonished]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "When the old man opened the door, to his surprise,",
      "prompt": "[surprised, astonished]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんが笠をかぶせてあげたお地蔵さまたちが、たくさん立っていました。",
      "prompt": "[astonished, amazed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "there stood many Jizo statues, the ones he had put hats on.",
      "prompt": "[astonished, amazed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そして、お地蔵さまは、おじいさんとおばあさんに、たくさんの宝物や、おいしい食べ物を運んできてくれたのです。",
      "prompt": "[amazed, grateful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "And the Jizo statues had brought them lots of treasures and delicious food.",
      "prompt": "[amazed, grateful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「これはどういうことだろう？」",
      "prompt": "[confused, amazed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page7_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"What could this mean?\"",
      "prompt": "[confused, amazed]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんとおばあさんは、びっくりしました。",
      "prompt": "[surprised, astonished]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The old man and woman were surprised.",
      "prompt": "[surprised, astonished]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "すると、お地蔵さまの中から一体のお地蔵さまが、にっこり笑って言いました。",
      "prompt": "[gentle, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Then, one of the Jizo statues smiled and said,",
      "prompt": "[gentle, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "「おじいさんの優しい心のおかげで、私たちもあたたかく過ごすことができました。",
      "prompt": "[warmly, gratefully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "\"Thanks to your kind heart, old man, we were able to stay warm.",
      "prompt": "[warmly, gratefully]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そのお礼に、この宝物をおじいさんとおばあさんにあげます。」",
      "prompt": "[generously, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page8_text4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "In return, we give these treasures to you and your wife.\"",
      "prompt": "[generously, kindly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんとおばあさんは、お地蔵さまに心から感謝しました。",
      "prompt": "[grateful, joyful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The old man and woman thanked the Jizo statues from the bottom of their hearts.",
      "prompt": "[grateful, joyful]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "そして、その宝物のおかげで、貧しい暮らしも楽になり、",
      "prompt": "[happily, relieved]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Thanks to those treasures, their poor life became easier,",
      "prompt": "[happily, relieved]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "その後はずっと幸せに暮らしましたとさ。",
      "prompt": "[happily, contentedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "page9_text3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "and they lived happily ever after.",
      "prompt": "[happily, contentedly]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question1_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんが町へ持っていったものは何ですか？食べ物、竹細工、お金",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question1_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the old man take to town? Food, Bamboo crafts, Money",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question2_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "おじいさんは、お地蔵さまに何をしてあげましたか？歌を歌ってあげた、笠をかぶせてあげた、お菓子をあげた",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question2_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the old man do for the Jizo statues? He sang them a song., He put hats on them., He gave them snacks.",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question3_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "笠が足りなくなったとき、おじいさんはどうしましたか？家に帰った、手ぬぐいをほどいてかぶせた、何もせずにお地蔵さまをそのままにした",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question3_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the old man do when he ran out of hats? He went home., He unraveled his towel and used it., He left the Jizo statues as they were.",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question4_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "夜、おじいさんとおばあさんの家の戸を鳴らしたのは誰でしたか？隣のおばあさん、お地蔵さまたち、町の人々",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question4_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Who knocked on the old couple's door at night? The old woman next door., The Jizo statues., People from town.",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question5_ja",
      "lang": "ja",
      "text": "お地蔵さまたちは、おじいさんとおばあさんに何を持ってきてくれましたか？野菜、宝物と食べ物、新しい笠",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    },
    {
      "audio": "question5_en",
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "What did the Jizo statues bring to the old man and woman? Vegetables, Treasures and food., New hats.",
      "prompt": "[question]"
    }
  ]
}